{"name":"Digest documents with Google Sheets and Twilio","nodes":[{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"wf05538-draft","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"2d04de31-b0a5-47cd-b509-3deb4a100f23","name":"Receive Inbound Webhook","webhookId":"760f868d-681d-41ff-9e40-009a1c47e1a1"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"2ff99fb3-a08c-450d-94df-cbd403c560ed","name":"draftId","value":"={{ $json.draftId || $json.id || $execution.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"66384ef9-62b7-4b51-9787-a1135917c4b0","name":"receivedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"1900b44c-2a92-4356-85b5-8288555495db","name":"Stamp & Shape Draft"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"912712a6-772a-4110-bdec-4e3cb576fb06","leftValue":"={{ $json.draftId }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[378,400],"id":"ad3a4ae3-a644-4e6c-892a-6999ad6c32f6","name":"Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[378,910],"id":"353f5d8f-8475-4cde-8bb4-acc6559b7c9b","name":"Record Rejected Input","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"promptType":"define","text":"={{ $json.chatInput || $json.topic || JSON.stringify($json) }}","options":{"systemMessage":"You are a social copy specialist for the content generation team. Use the attached tools to look up real data before answering — never invent draft details. Keep answers under 150 words, cite which tool you used, and escalate anything you cannot verify.","maxIterations":8}},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[702,400],"id":"aa32379a-1115-465a-bfe6-cfe4fcbb69d4","name":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"model":"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5","options":{}},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenRouter","typeVersion":1,"position":[945,970],"id":"76a07830-f4b3-441d-bf71-ce2d468716f2","name":"OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.toolCalculator","typeVersion":1,"position":[945,1390],"id":"8213f64a-ddfb-4297-83eb-190d92c96f00","name":"Run Calculations"},{"parameters":{"toolDescription":"Fetch live draft data from the internal REST API by id or query.","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/drafts","options":{}},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.toolHttpRequest","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[1174,1390],"id":"fdd08e54-efbc-4502-810a-7f8bb2f061a1","name":"Lookup API Data"},{"parameters":{},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.toolThink","typeVersion":1,"position":[1633,1390],"id":"d340bc9a-912a-4b45-97c5-420110383f8c","name":"Think It Through"},{"parameters":{"sessionIdType":"customKey","sessionKey":"={{ $json.sessionId || $execution.id }}","contextWindowLength":12},"type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.memoryBufferWindow","typeVersion":1.3,"position":[1390,970],"id":"ca0f1288-fb81-436f-82c8-8f908eae30c4","name":"Conversation Memory"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"e57f80e0-f16f-462f-bba2-4496783989d2","name":"answer","value":"={{ $json.output }}","type":"string"},{"id":"2a35041d-96f6-4cfd-8bbc-f61e0fc8db90","name":"confidence","value":"={{ $json.output && $json.output.length > 40 ? 'high' : 'low' }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[1957,400],"id":"33d453b1-93f2-48c0-8633-8b9d27128917","name":"Shape Agent Output"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"346e522b-30c2-4db3-9adf-c99c58ac6db6","leftValue":"={{ $json.confidence }}","rightValue":"high","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"equals"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[2281,400],"id":"fd7a8cea-c8c3-45fa-b01e-e5a93d1162c7","name":"Confident Enough?"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[2605,160],"id":"4cd09867-35ae-4ca1-9279-dd9764345d14","name":"Deliver Answer + Log to Google Sheets","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#content","cachedResultName":"#content"},"text":"=🙋 Low-confidence answer needs review: {{ $json.answer }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[2929,760],"id":"045753b6-41b4-4abc-8eb8-425f60133d38","name":"Escalate to Human Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[3577,400],"id":"1b959528-dfbd-49dd-a4a1-bec632600263","name":"Join Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[4549,400],"id":"2de4ee13-245c-4bab-a000-e427c37e73a2","name":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[4873,400],"id":"25998f1c-91c9-4bac-b35c-4bf5c76a9305","name":"Archive Row Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"74b530ff-1cfa-4c5d-8d35-2bcea44b3879","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"16d72b64-3378-4cb1-a5e2-cc537d116794","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"ee8a01c4-4caa-4244-b934-35ca1c6bec21","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5197,400],"id":"8f61d21b-e30a-4ed2-a63e-4b090d421cfe","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5521,400],"id":"bb1e7365-1395-4598-95ea-4c644fb0cdb4","name":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#content","cachedResultName":"#content"},"text":"=✅ Digest documents with Google Sheets and Twilio — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5845,400],"id":"24cdacb4-d777-418b-ac83-854ac09255a8","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"e071eb61-4afb-4218-afdd-25db13dfe2e5","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"227d89b6-88b4-4b1d-8fda-36a10e3db24a","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"ba32cca5-4f32-42d5-9c7b-2e6935b64a51","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5197,1420],"id":"97825651-6d34-4103-b7f2-9e05994727ea","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#content","cachedResultName":"#content"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5521,1420],"id":"fa10dcc0-5fd0-43d9-a457-1db43840f71b","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Draft Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5845,1420],"id":"9dcf2dd1-8fb2-4b72-a0a9-9040c7133ded","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf05538-draft`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Draft","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"48b4235d-ce2e-195c-30e4-a33bf528ac6c","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Draft\n\nShapes the item: writes `draftId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"76f86acf-db36-c623-e55a-a9aa065cd343","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Draft"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.draftId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reason & Act (AI Agent) · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"ee7a1ca7-d52b-e651-3c34-39dc44ccba46","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"d5c35847-2624-7f6e-934c-66d1907d4079","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reason & Act (AI Agent)\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Shape Agent Output · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"496f699d-1752-ff8f-58b3-6d49b1f03039","name":"Note: Reason & Act (AI Agent)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"a348e3bd-14dc-b14f-5af1-a77819e1f483","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Run Calculations\n\nMath tool — keeps arithmetic exact instead of letting the LLM guess.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1510],"id":"d4d66d58-9c19-bf71-2177-58cc29a19b1d","name":"Note: Run Calculations"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Lookup API Data\n\nTool the agent can call to hit the REST API with parameters it chooses at runtime.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1114,1750],"id":"e6afa0a4-618a-c8fb-0ed5-deaf163262e6","name":"Note: Lookup API Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Think It Through\n\nScratchpad tool: lets the agent reason step-by-step before acting.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1573,1510],"id":"2ca6a84a-a39c-57e8-1abf-d72ec1ef0753","name":"Note: Think It Through"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Conversation Memory\n\nConversation memory keyed by session — the bot remembers earlier turns for each user separately.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `memory`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1330,1090],"id":"dbb0d572-7576-2ef7-a701-d146fb489ebb","name":"Note: Conversation Memory"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Shape Agent Output\n\nShapes the item: writes `answer`, `confidence`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Confident Enough?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1897,520],"id":"5febd88e-6dd9-236d-6a3f-004517444aad","name":"Note: Shape Agent Output"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Confident Enough?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.confidence }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Deliver Answer + Log to Google Sheets · ②→ Escalate to Human Queue","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2221,520],"id":"d22fae5d-e76a-5aab-5a4e-5fb4ba0cab9f","name":"Note: Confident Enough?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Deliver Answer + Log to Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2545,280],"id":"c1e3bcf5-d315-26c4-005c-d42659ce2e6e","name":"Note: Deliver Answer + Log to Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate to Human Queue\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2869,880],"id":"d1824c3e-74ce-3707-453a-c6d482c44ecb","name":"Note: Escalate to Human Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Join Outcomes\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3517,520],"id":"c28862d0-ab47-620d-76cf-82683769cfa9","name":"Note: Join Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4489,520],"id":"e562e8d6-1209-aa24-f5fc-6b773eadc1de","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4813,520],"id":"12c69db3-f90d-0591-4214-0b0f621c6dc4","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5137,520],"id":"ccf2aebb-da00-8f54-7246-96af7e5890d0","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5461,520],"id":"1f46e31b-24e5-6b4a-6ed7-9d8071c00320","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5785,520],"id":"3e93092b-09bf-f6bb-c7e2-1fd7f24beb10","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5137,1540],"id":"69e1b0b1-2439-f5d1-8dd7-5fcdf8f9a292","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5461,1540],"id":"d8ed0a7b-1844-d75b-da9a-a6b2dd328ccf","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5785,1540],"id":"7815fc21-7525-cbd8-e8e6-9d8dcb22a492","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Digest documents with Google Sheets and Twilio\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest documents with Google Sheets and Twilio. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual social copy is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Draft → Payload Valid? → Reason & Act (AI Agent) → Shape Agent Output → Confident Enough? → Deliver Answer + Log to Google Sheets → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating social copy in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Responds in seconds\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"db2c6a49-7cc3-a222-0332-d381c9623a26","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"96cddb98-af76-1c9d-d296-72da5b8032bc","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"9260edb0-2acf-e205-38ee-a1b826d6790e","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"c2eceb7e-b00e-aebf-15c6-94d60498bc8d","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your social copy process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"185fd3e2-0d97-c889-42c9-a1158dbc0d2a","